Comment.val: /*Function to get the Fiscal attest 281.60 information.*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: select t.tr_volgnummer, t.tr_notabedrag, t.tr_rel1_rek2_munts from transactions t inner join Rekeningen_Per_Product rpp on rpp.rpp_relatienummer=t.tr_rel1 and rpp.rpp_rekening_nummer=t.tr_rel1_rek2 and rpp.rpp_rekeningsoort=t.tr_rel1_rek2_soort and rpp.rpp_valuta=t.tr_rel1_rek2_munts where t.tr_indicatie = 'O-G' and t.tr_mutatiecode = ~1 and t.tr_transdatum between ~2 and ~3 and rpp.rpp_relatienummer=~4 and rpp.rpp_productnummer=~5 and rpp.rpp_volgnr_per_product=~6

select t.tr_volgnummer, t.tr_notabedrag, t.tr_rel2_rek2_munts from transactions t inner join Rekeningen_Per_Product rpp on rpp.rpp_relatienummer=t.tr_rel2 and rpp.rpp_rekening_nummer=t.tr_rel2_rek2 and rpp.rpp_rekeningsoort=t.tr_rel2_rek2_soort and rpp.rpp_valuta=t.tr_rel2_rek2_munts where t.tr_indicatie = 'O-G' and t.tr_mutatiecode = ~1 and t.tr_transdatum between ~2 and ~3 and rpp.rpp_relatienummer=~4 and rpp.rpp_productnummer=~5 and rpp.rpp_volgnr_per_product=~6
